 Nigerian actor, Alex Ekubo has finally announced the date for his traditional wedding and his white wedding with his fiancee, Fancy. In the early hours of yesterday, May 10th, Alex Ekubo disclosed that he will be announcing the date for his wedding ceremony with his fiancee. Alex Ekubo has taken to his page to share the marriage invitation between himself and his fiancee, Fancy. According to the marriage invitation, the ceremony will take place on the 20th and 27th of November, 2021. The date chosen by the couple has got a lot of people talking. Many are of the opinion that the date shouldn’t have been announced since it’s far while many also express shock that the wedding wasn’t going to take place soon.